Analysis complete. Card moved to **Ready for plan review**.

**Summary**: Issue #101 is a confirmed bug — `principal_type` (and `description`) are defined in the `role_assignments` variable but never referenced in the `azurerm_role_assignment` resource block. PR #102 attempted a fix and was merged, but its changes were lost (the PR diff contained merge conflict markers). The proposed fix is to add `principal_type = each.value.principal_type` and `description = each.value.description` to the resource block in `main.tf`.


